          .col-md-6(style='padding-top: 10%;')
            h1 Student Options
            h5 Next to students names will be three options. The first is the Program Of Study. Here you will be able to view the students full work towards their degree based on catalog year. The second option is the Program Planner where you can view the layout of all four years in a more time oriented manner. The last option is the Archives. The archives will not open unless a student has archives to view. Once you submit a Program Of Study you will then be able to view archives that are name stamped with a date and time to the minute.
        .row
          .col-md-6(style='padding-top: 12%;')
            img(src='/assets/home/navbar1.png', alt='Picture Not Found', width='60%', height='90%')
          .col-md-6(style='padding-top: 12%;')
            h1 Add Student & Course Loading View
            h5 You have two options to choose from. You can add a student by uploading their DARS report which must list your ohio email address. Or you can view the Course Loading View to see the project students for each ETM course. The Course Loading view is also accessible from the Program Of Study & Program Planner.
        .row
